{"tid":2231670,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[亮劍]日本: 要求中國刪除釣魚島專題網站","createTime":"2020-10-05T23:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T00:40:26.000Z","uid":204533,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e567cb11477d88e31482c9a10541adbc6b89e421","tid":2231670,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本官房長官加藤勝信在10月5日午前的記者會上，就中國國家海洋局所屬&ldquo;國家海洋情報中心&rdquo;，10月3日開始，釣魚島數字博物館在釣魚島專題網站（<a href=\"http://www.diaoyudao.org.cn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.diaoyudao.org.cn&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL6pJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=ad3415c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.diaoyudao.org.cn</a>）正式開通上線表示，已通過外交渠道要求中國政府削除該網站。<br />\n<br />\n加藤指出：中國方面沒有將我國固有的領土尖閣諸島做成網頁的理由。<strong><span class=\"red\">這種基於中國方面單方面的主張是完全不可接受的。</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20201005-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4%E9%87%A3%E9%AD%9A%E5%B3%B6%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20201005-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2588%25AA%25E9%2599%25A4%25E9%2587%25A3%25E9%25AD%259A%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A1%258C%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25AB%2599&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL6pJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=b7a266e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20201005-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4%E9%87%A3%E9%AD%9A%E5%B3%B6%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99</a>"},{"pid":"aebe4516a3977735b7d73d30cfbb08e8ed204e41","tid":2231670,"uid":204533,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:13:56.000Z","msg":"又想拉攏日本, 又派王毅去日本<br />\n點知未去就玩野, 你估咁人地就驚咩?<br />\n戰狼外交真心好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9040787d5835792e2af14